00:40:01,750 --> 00:40:03,115
I promise.

771
00:40:06,671 --> 00:40:08,787
You've got five minutes.

772
00:40:08,823 --> 00:40:10,663
Thank you. That's all I need.

773
00:40:43,691 --> 00:40:45,118
We manufacture
everything ourselves,

774
00:40:45,142 --> 00:40:46,742
right here, in Atlanta.

775
00:40:46,778 --> 00:40:49,762
<i>We import nothing from China.</i>

776
00:40:51,849 --> 00:40:55,584
<i>This isn't a job to me.</i>

777
00:40:55,619 --> 00:40:57,470
This is my calling.

778
00:41:09,534 --> 00:41:11,234
Oh, my God.

779
00:41:21,145 --> 00:41:24,363
What happened to you?

780
00:41:24,399 --> 00:41:28,251
The question should be
what didn't happen to me.

781
00:41:30,037 --> 00:41:31,370
I have had

782
00:41:31,406 --> 00:41:33,723
some pretty terrible days

783
00:41:33,758 --> 00:41:35,508
as a doctor, but today

784
00:41:35,543 --> 00:41:38,828
just might take the prize.

785
00:41:38,863 --> 00:41:42,631
That looks really swollen.

786
00:41:42,667 --> 00:41:44,583
Are you sure you're okay?

787
00:41:47,855 --> 00:41:51,157
Today, I got kicked around.

788
00:41:51,192 --> 00:41:53,192
Abused.

789
00:41:53,227 --> 00:41:55,110
Unappreciated.

790
00:41:57,882 --> 00:42:00,966
At times, I just felt
completely useless.

791
00:42:01,001 --> 00:42:04,420
Then come with
me to San Francisco.

792
00:42:09,928 --> 00:42:12,645
It's not easy.

793
00:42:12,680 --> 00:42:14,325
If it were,

794
00:42:14,349 --> 00:42:16,332
everyone would be a doctor,

795
00:42:16,367 --> 00:42:20,103
because it is the
best job in the world.

796
00:42:20,138 --> 00:42:22,338
Despite everything.

797
00:42:22,373 --> 00:42:26,225
Because of everything.

798
00:42:26,260 --> 00:42:30,162
I wouldn't trade my worst
day at Chastain for my best

799
00:42:30,198 --> 00:42:33,449
making medical
devices in Silicon Valley.

800
00:42:41,792 --> 00:42:44,727
I can't leave.

801
00:42:45,763 --> 00:42:48,147
I'm sorry.

802
00:42:53,922 --> 00:42:57,523
But, hey, hey...

803
00:42:57,558 --> 00:42:59,258
this doesn't mean

804
00:42:59,293 --> 00:43:02,061
that I don't want to figure
out how to make this work.

805
00:43:04,599 --> 00:43:07,233
But is it really what you want?

806
